ERROR REACHED MAX 300 RECORDS! PLEASE FIX ERRORS..            05
PRESS F5 FOR NEXT STEP, OR F3 TO GO BACK..                    06
FIX ERROR AND TRY AGAIN..                                     07
BIN# SHOILD BE 01 - 99!                                       08
USER PART IS NOT IN OUR SYSTEM! PLEASE REGISTER...            09
QUANTITY IS INVALID!                                          10
ORDER# SHOULD NOT BE BLANK!                                   11
DELIVERY DATE IS INVALID!                                     12
Q/C IS INVALID!                                               13
MULTIPLE DELIVERY CODES ARE NOT ACCEPTABL!                    14
USER PART IS NOT IN SHIPPING MASTER!                          15
THERE IS NO ORDER DATA TO BE UPLOADED!                        16
SHIPPING MASTER IS NOT SET UP!                                17
SHIP DATE IS EARLIER THAN TODAY!                              18
ORDER ALREADY EXISTS! (WILL BE DUPLICATED)                    19
